1. RESOLVED — Patient portal can view and pay for prescription orders.
   The patient order payment section treats visible, unpaid, non-cancelled prescription orders as payable.

2. RESOLVED — Link supplier to item supports bulk suppliers, per-supplier pricing, and non-inventory items.
   Supplier Management's Bulk Link Items modal now supports inventory and non-inventory item linking, multiple suppliers, per-supplier pricing, and spreadsheet bulk uploads for inventory/non-inventory supplier products.
